{"tid":2435621,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[公審學校]唔睇fb唔知依家啲家長真係咁撚痴線","createTime":"2021-03-06T11:26:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T13:08:53.000Z","uid":242444,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"273c52814175a0848fb6de051e98bc4aefcca03a","tid":2435621,"uid":242444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T11:26:10.000Z","msg":"五個小孩的校方迫完學生退學再兇查詢既家長出律師信<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2429239\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2429239</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n個樓主話因為唔填監護人比學校勸退<br />\n心諗咁小事點會叫你走<br />\n睇睇下個樓主原來係痴撚線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T307xH2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT307xH2.png&h=fe732149&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v2jTtgP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv2jTtgP.png&h=c52f0cd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲話已經告到去教育局唔鬥死個校長唔罷休咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ls4j8hd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLs4j8hd.png&h=293b46a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事主本人fb仲有勁多人撐佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/652388971/posts/10158943096868972/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F652388971%2Fposts%2F10158943096868972%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n5LurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=552eecf7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/652388971/posts/10158943096868972/?d=n</a><br />\n洪曉嫻你想搞大件事呀嘛<br />\n宜家幫你<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aUn2mCV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaUn2mCV.png&h=cc7e5173&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"642f778d353086c13cc101f7edfa861cd11f16fd","tid":2435621,"uid":242444,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T11:30:29.000Z","msg":"洪曉嫻同佢班癲雞點解咁抗拒填監護人呢？？？？<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>大家了解一下樓主（洪曉嫻）<br />\n其實佢都唔係未試過一離開同溫層就畀人屌到飛天<img src=